precis:
Regulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1113) which set limits
(Maximum Residue Limit) on residues of "GLUFOSINATE-AMMONIUM" in lentils,
rapeseed (canola), dry white beans and potatoes and in the liver and
kidneys of cattle, goats, hogs, poultry and sheep.
